contentrichtext.text: '''KBBL''' may refer to: * [[KBBL (The Simpsons)]], fictional radio and television stations featured in ''The Simpsons'' * [[KBBL-LP]], a television station (channel 56) licensed to serve Springfield, Missouri, United States, translator of KWBM * [[KXNW]], a television station (channel 34) licensed to serve Eureka Springs, Arkansas, United States, which used the call sign KBBL-TV from July 2006 to September 2006 * [[KWNL-CD]], a television station (channel 9) licensed to serve Winslow, Arkansas, which used the call sign KBBL-CA from September 2003 to July 2006 * a former radio station in Little Rock, Arkansas, hometown of [[Equity Broadcasting]]; that station, rather than ''The Simpsons'', was probably the inspiration for the KBBL-CA call letters{{fact|date=May 2011}} {{Disambiguation|callsign}}
